results.name: Expansion of Product_{i=0..m-1} (1 + x^(2*i+1)) for m=11.
comment: Product_{i=0..m-1} (1 + x^(2*i+1)) is the Poincaré polynomial for GL(m).
Number of self-conjugate partitions of n into at most 11 parts. Also, number of partitions of n into distinct odd parts not larger than 21. - _Álvar Ibeas_, Aug 01 2020
reference: H. Weyl, The Classical Groups, Princeton, 1946, see p. 233.
link: Nathaniel Johnston, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..121 (full sequence)
